Gordon Brothers unlock opportunity on both sides of the balance sheet. In times of growth, change, and challenge, we create custom solutions to unlock liquidity, and provide flexibility to owners, operators and their lenders. For more than a century, we have innovated, elevated and honed strategies to identify and extract value from underperforming assets through hands on management and capital solutions, across retail and industrial and heavy equipment sectors. Our disposition services span inventory, plant and equipment, real estate, receivables and intellectual property. We work with healthy, stressed and distressed businesses, at all points in the business lifecycle, whether that means growth or strategic consolidation, providing certainty on results both financially and operationally. Talk with Gordon Brothers today to unlock your balance sheet and move business forward.